snippet.title: FINAL FANTASY XI – Opening movie
snippet.description:
FINAL FANTASY XI is the first online game in the award-winning FINAL FANTASY series. 
Set out on your own adventure to discover endless deep secrets of Vana’diel!   
Check out more: http://www.playonline.com/ff11us/
